Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭從未結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行星聯盟宇宙軍以及拉爾康帝國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都假設戰爭將會來臨而開始備戰的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續創下歷史性勝利的驅逐艦微風號的乘員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接獲軍司令部之命到地上執勤兼度假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短暫的休憩時間流逝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳選擇什麼當聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點超出預算\N我想用領帶就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,領帶嗎，這比較實在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，我也買領帶好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們約幾點見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們提早下班，一起去買東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我\N什麼嘛，是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦，要有草莓的那種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會買回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕夜嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，聖誕夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨，資料課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史塔少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很有精神在做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過因為這是資料課…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.00,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?艦長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來這招啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.52,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，你在叫我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.02,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，艦長\N打擾你工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.73,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個… 我是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上你有空嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚一起進餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.81,0:03:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，知道了\N七點在"花園"見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，待會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀，聖誕夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕夜?那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.26,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…這…\N今晚是聖誕夜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你們倆才一起用餐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.45,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，跑哪去了\N有了有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次尾牙玩賓果贏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人份餐廳招待卷，阿里巴巴餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.59,0:04:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿里巴巴餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山本你應該來參加尾牙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.17,0:04:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那時候我忙著替艦長加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我去一趟就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.69,0:04:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿拉伯料理我還沒吃過\N太令人期待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能會不合史塔少校的口味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.75,0:04:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我最喜歡的是中華料理…\N算了，也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山本你打算做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟海兵隊的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起喝酒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，聖誕夜嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好，聽起來很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一起去慶祝怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也找史塔少校來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是，就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃完後再去會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到吃完後嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在老地方是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想最後應該會去"火男"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那麼到時見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在"火男"哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜他八成不會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.38,0:06:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把這個交給情報局的卡爾森少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是她訂的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要交給卡爾森少校哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個孩子是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.94,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.55,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是蛋糕有這麼重嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.03,0:06:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不太像蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是30公分大的方形盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以小熊花紋的包裝紙包起來\N包得很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼包裝紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熊花紋，小熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想真的是炸彈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.26,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聖誕節利用小孩子送定時炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是專家的常見手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，說不定開箱的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 真的嗎\N- 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.41,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是聖誕夜\N這點打扮是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服我明天來拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我會保管好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借、借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的交給你了，山本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不抓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.27,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼，這…\N我是說蛋糕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.77,0:10:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情鬧得那麼大，大家太小題大作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我想應該已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.71,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通人是會把我捉起來\N帶去警察局的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.61,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，那只是小小的惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.58,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以說，你們大人不是被人稍微捉弄一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就很生氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.79,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再教訓我，以後不能做這種事\N不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後說已經很晚了\N再不快點回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.16,0:11:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家裡的媽媽會擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕，要遲到了\N再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.28,0:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回家去吧，你媽在擔心你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算回家，家裡又沒有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.35,0:11:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是叫我回家嗎\N因為很晚了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人都是這樣的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.77,0:12:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等很久了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼拉我上電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心的啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底要跟到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走的方向，剛好跟你一樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.64,0:13:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小哥，那邊的小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.47,0:13:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小哥，怎樣\N買禮物送給女朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.48,0:13:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會算你便宜的\N你看這個好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒有加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明說好是七點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不覺被強迫買下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，送給由理子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不可能跟上來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛，又是定時炸彈嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是真的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你叫那小鬼偷的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒良心的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然利用小孩子\N走，上法院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.92,0:15:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過你要是現在肯付錢\N我就放你一馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.49,0:15:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，我付，我付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，你不吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭，真難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.33,0:15:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在外面吃東西，太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕宴會嗎，真豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔要不要也來，一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以讓我加入嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣，吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還有這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡面裝的是葡萄酒\N在三丁目餐廳後門找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真能幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好喝的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試試…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.03,0:16:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個叔叔…不是正常人\N怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕，由理子在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼，有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就現在解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等大路旁的櫻花開了\N下次再一起賞花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大鬧一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那還要我能平安渡過今年冬天才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔叔們，保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要回家了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.49,0:18:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑰匙，我家鑰匙不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…居然兩人一起用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我了解我了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是，這傢伙酒品真差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那張臉，憑什麼跟女人共餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.49,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是軍隊那裡出事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.42,0:18:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑個時髦點的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是聖誕夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，一定要"火男"\N一定要去"火男"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不到…\N被人撿走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.58,0:19:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好從總部那條路找起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.98,0:19:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，我一個人找就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.35,0:19:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人找比一個人找要來的快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.98,0:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再找仔細點，一定找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不必的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.22,0:19:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑰匙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑰匙在管理員那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼，原來如此\N太好了太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.08,0:20:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 我沒事\N- 我看你很糟呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿里巴巴…進餐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們要吃到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，再來一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是氣喘病發作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不需要移動醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這兒睡一晚就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是誰家的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，我還沒問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家裡的人大概在擔心他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問情報局卡爾森少校的連絡處是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.92,0:21:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我轉給他好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.23,0:21:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說我兒子在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.74,0:21:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是卡爾森少校嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.14,0:21:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.81,0:22:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心，他睡得很熟\N在這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.86,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必謝我，謝他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.67,0:22:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，小犬添你麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.50,0:22:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.17,0:22:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，他怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.47,0:22:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他跟我開聖誕宴會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.55,0:22:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕宴會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N傍晚的騷動是這孩子引起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會教訓他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.00,0:22:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.63,0:23:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罵他之前，妳這做母親的\N該想想孩子做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.57,0:23:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像講的太酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.21,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得沒錯，原因可能出在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我轉告他，下次一起去賞花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼，今晚你不陪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.66,0:23:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼突然急著走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳踏車借一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.25,0:23:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.05,0:23:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕節快樂，鮑伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.24,0:25:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.75,0:25:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會積雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.49,0:26:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由理子

